# Local history (optional, but keep it tracked in Git repository to allow GitHub Actions to commit and persist it, so we don't ignore meal_history.json unless they want to keep it local only. However, to prevent local development testing from polluting Git, the user can choose. We will track meal_history.json by default but ignore environment files and caches.)
